title: Empowering Thoughts

description:
Episode 439 - How do you speak to yourself in your own head? Do you use empowering words or do you talk down to yourself? The most important conversation that you will ever have is the on you have between yourself. In this episode, I'm going to dive into the strategies to build yourself and become happier.
